1773<h3>

1774<strong>

1775What’s Your Ideal Design for the Bathroom Vanity?</strong>

1776</h3>

1777

1778<p>

1779When looking to change up your bathroom’s style, or looking for a light remodel, there are three main components to look at.</p>

1780

1781<ul>

1782

1783 <li>

1784<strong>

1785Vanity cabinets — </strong>

1786These cabinets make a statement in the bathroom as one of the main fixtures. Styles are available in various sizes, colors, and designs.&nbsp;</li>

1787

1788 <li>

1789<strong>

1790Bathroom accessories —</strong>

1791 For organization, function, and style, accessories are the finishing touches that make or break the design.&nbsp;</li>

1792

1793 <li>

1794<strong>

1795Vanity mirrors —</strong>

1796 Mirror, much like cabinets, can be major statement pieces. Available in a selection of styles, shapes, sizes, and finishes so you can make the statement you want.&nbsp;</li>

1797

1798</ul>

1799

1800<p>

1801Browse our selection of vanity cabinets and accessories now to find the perfect style for your home.</p>
